<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Fluvial processes rather than fire primarily disturb stands. Stands are disturbed by different flooding regimes in natural tidal marshes, or by artificial manipulation of brackish marshes through disking, burning, seeding, and shifting flooding regimes.</div>
